# pyproject.toml here only holds ruff/pytest/coverage config, not PEP 621
# package metadata -- Vercel's Python builder treats any pyproject.toml as
# a project manifest and runs `uv lock` against it, which fails without a
# [project] table. requirements.txt is our actual dependency source and is
# already supported directly by Vercel, so just don't upload this file.
pyproject.toml
